entries.journal_entry_description: Boba Fett has decided to let you do his dirty work and take out 3 bounty targets who are known associates of Vladlun Travan.
entries.journal_entry_title: Boba Fett Throws You To the Wolves
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Boba Fett has bounties for three criminals known to be associates of Vladlun Travan
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Return to Boba Fett. If you're lucky, he might even pay you for your efforts.
